# Team Plan Availability гғӘгғ•гӮЎгӮҜгӮҝгғӘгғігӮ°д»•ж§ҳжӣё v2пјҲFlutter жә–жӢ зүҲпјү

## жҰӮиҰҒ

`Team` гғўгғҮгғ«гҒ®еҲӨе®ҡгғӯгӮёгғғгӮҜгӮ’ Flutter гӮўгғ—гғӘгҒ®иЁӯиЁҲгҒ«е®Ңе…ЁгҒ«еҗҲгӮҸгҒӣгӮӢгҖӮе‘ҪеҗҚгҖҒenum гҒ®дҪҝз”ЁгҖҒgetter гҒ®ж§ӢйҖ гӮ’гҒҷгҒ№гҒҰ Flutter гҒЁзөұдёҖгҒ—гҖҒWeb гҒЁгғўгғҗгӮӨгғ«гҒ§дёҖиІ«гҒ—гҒҹе®ҹиЈ…гӮ’е®ҹзҸҫгҒҷгӮӢгҖӮ

## иғҢжҷҜ

### зҸҫеңЁгҒ®е•ҸйЎҢ
- Web гҒЁ Flutter гҒ§е‘ҪеҗҚгҒҢз•°гҒӘгӮӢпјҲ`currentTotalBallUsage` vs `ballUsage`пјү
- Web гҒҜ object + booleanгҖҒFlutter гҒҜ enum гҒ§зҠ¶ж…ӢгӮ’иЎЁзҸҫ
- getter гҒ®ж§ӢйҖ гҒҢз•°гҒӘгӮҠгҖҒгӮігғјгғүгғ¬гғ“гғҘгғјжҷӮгҒ«ж··д№ұгҒҢз”ҹгҒҳгӮӢ

### зӣ®жЁҷ
- **е®Ңе…ЁгҒӘе‘ҪеҗҚзөұдёҖ**пјҡFlutter гҒЁеҗҢгҒҳе‘ҪеҗҚиҰҸеүҮгӮ’дҪҝз”Ё
- **enum гғҷгғјгӮ№гҒ®иЁӯиЁҲ**пјҡTypeScript гҒ§ Flutter гҒ® enum гӮ’еҶҚзҸҫ
- **дёҖиІ«гҒ—гҒҹ API**пјҡWeb гҒЁ Flutter гҒ§еҗҢгҒҳ getter еҗҚгғ»жҲ»гӮҠеҖӨж§ӢйҖ 

## Flutter гҒ®иЁӯиЁҲпјҲеҸӮз…§е…ғпјү

### Dart гӮігғјгғүпјҲжҠңзІӢпјү

```dart
class Team {
  // дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸиЁҲз®—
  int get ballUsage {
    final planUsage = (teamPlan?.withinPeriod ?? false)
      ? teamPlan?.currentUsage ?? 0
      : 0;
    final itemUsage = item?.ballUsage ?? 0;
    return planUsage + itemUsage;
  }

  int get maxBalls {
    final planMax = (teamPlan?.withinPeriod ?? false)
      ? teamPlan?.plan?.maxBalls ?? 0
      : 0;
    final itemMax = item?.ballAvailableCount ?? 0;
    return planMax + itemMax;
  }

  // зҠ¶ж…ӢеҲӨе®ҡпјҲenumпјү
  TeamPlanStatus get teamPlanStatus { /* ... */ }
  BallAnalysisUsageStatus get ballAnalysisUsageStatus { /* ... */ }

  // еҲ©з”ЁеҸҜеҗҰеҲӨе®ҡ
  bool get canAnalyzeBall {
    return ballAnalysisUsageStatus.canAnalyze;
  }
}

// enum е®ҡзҫ©
enum TeamPlanStatus {
  noContract,       // жңүж–ҷгғ—гғ©гғіеҘ‘зҙ„гҒӘгҒ—
  nextPlanPending,  // ж¬Ўеӣһгғ—гғ©гғігҒҢдҝқз•ҷдёӯ
  expired,          // жңҹйҷҗеҲҮгӮҢ
  expiringSoon,     // 30ж—Ҙд»ҘеҶ…гҒ«жңҹйҷҗеҲҮгӮҢ
  ok,               // жӯЈеёё
}

enum BallAnalysisUsageStatus {
  limitReached,     // дёҠйҷҗеҲ°йҒ”
  limitApproaching, // дёҠйҷҗжҺҘиҝ‘пјҲ90%д»ҘдёҠпјү
  ok,               // жӯЈеёё
}
```

## Web еҒҙгҒ®ж–°иЁӯиЁҲ

### 1. enum гҒ®е®ҡзҫ©

**ж–°иҰҸгғ•гӮЎгӮӨгғ«пјҡ`web/src/models/team-status.ts`**

```typescript
/**
 * гғҒгғјгғ гғ—гғ©гғігҒ®еҘ‘зҙ„гғ»жңүеҠ№жңҹйҷҗгҒ«й–ўгҒҷгӮӢзҠ¶ж…Ӣ
 * Flutter гҒ® TeamPlanStatus гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
export enum TeamPlanStatus {
  NO_CONTRACT = 'no_contract',        // жңүж–ҷгғ—гғ©гғіеҘ‘зҙ„гҒӘгҒ—
  NEXT_PLAN_PENDING = 'next_plan_pending',  // ж¬Ўеӣһгғ—гғ©гғігҒҢдҝқз•ҷдёӯ
  EXPIRED = 'expired',                // жңҹйҷҗеҲҮгӮҢ
  EXPIRING_SOON = 'expiring_soon',    // 30ж—Ҙд»ҘеҶ…гҒ«жңҹйҷҗеҲҮгӮҢ
  OK = 'ok',                          // жӯЈеёё
}

/**
 * гғңгғјгғ«и§ЈжһҗгҒ®дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸзҠ¶ж…Ӣ
 * Flutter гҒ® BallAnalysisUsageStatus гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
export enum BallUsageStatus {
  LIMIT_REACHED = 'limit_reached',      // дёҠйҷҗеҲ°йҒ”
  LIMIT_APPROACHING = 'limit_approaching',  // дёҠйҷҗжҺҘиҝ‘пјҲ90%д»ҘдёҠпјү
  OK = 'ok',                            // жӯЈеёё
}

/**
 * AI гӮігғјгғҒгҒ®дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸзҠ¶ж…Ӣ
 * Flutter гҒ® AICoachUsageStatus гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
export enum AiCoachUsageStatus {
  LIMIT_REACHED = 'limit_reached',
  LIMIT_APPROACHING = 'limit_approaching',
  OK = 'ok',
}

// Helper functions
export const teamPlanStatusIsValid = (status: TeamPlanStatus): boolean => {
  return status === TeamPlanStatus.EXPIRING_SOON || status === TeamPlanStatus.OK;
};

export const ballUsageStatusCanAnalyze = (status: BallUsageStatus): boolean => {
  return status === BallUsageStatus.LIMIT_APPROACHING || status === BallUsageStatus.OK;
};

export const ballUsageStatusShouldWarn = (status: BallUsageStatus): boolean => {
  return status === BallUsageStatus.LIMIT_APPROACHING;
};

export const aiCoachUsageStatusCanUse = (status: AiCoachUsageStatus): boolean => {
  return status === AiCoachUsageStatus.LIMIT_APPROACHING || status === AiCoachUsageStatus.OK;
};
```

### 2. Team гғўгғҮгғ«гҒ®дҝ®жӯЈ

**`web/src/models/team.ts`**

#### 2.1 дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸиЁҲз®—гҒ® getterпјҲе‘ҪеҗҚеӨүжӣҙпјү

**еӨүжӣҙеүҚпјҡ**
```typescript
get currentTotalBallUsage(): number | undefined
get currentTotalBallAvailableCount(): number | undefined
get currentTotalAiCoachUsage(): number | undefined
get currentTotalAiCoachAvailableCount(): number | undefined
```

**еӨүжӣҙеҫҢпјҡ**
```typescript
/**
 * гғңгғјгғ«и§ЈжһҗгҒ®дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸпјҲTeamPlan + Item гҒ®еҗҲз®—пјү
 * Flutter гҒ® ballUsage гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get ballUsage(): number {
  if (!this.teamPlan && !this.item) {
    return 0;
  }
  const planUsage = this.teamPlanAvailability.isAvailable
    ? this.teamPlan?.currentUsage ?? 0
    : 0;
  const itemUsage = this.item?.ballUsage ?? 0;
  return planUsage + itemUsage;
}

/**
 * гғңгғјгғ«и§ЈжһҗгҒ®дёҠйҷҗж•°пјҲTeamPlan + Item гҒ®еҗҲз®—пјү
 * Flutter гҒ® maxBalls гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get maxBalls(): number {
  if (!this.teamPlan && !this.item) {
    return 0;
  }
  const planMax = this.teamPlanAvailability.isAvailable
    ? this.teamPlan?.plan.maxBalls ?? 0
    : 0;
  const itemMax = this.item?.ballAvailableCount ?? 0;
  return planMax + itemMax;
}

/**
 * AI гӮігғјгғҒгҒ®дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸпјҲTeamPlan + Item гҒ®еҗҲз®—пјү
 * Flutter гҒ® aiCoachUsage гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get aiCoachUsage(): number {
  if (!this.teamPlan && !this.item) {
    return 0;
  }
  const planUsage = this.teamPlanAvailability.isAvailable
    ? this.teamPlan?.currentAiCoachUsage ?? 0
    : 0;
  const itemUsage = this.item?.aiCoachUsage ?? 0;
  return planUsage + itemUsage;
}

/**
 * AI гӮігғјгғҒгҒ®дёҠйҷҗж•°пјҲTeamPlan + Item гҒ®еҗҲз®—пјү
 * Flutter гҒ® maxAICoachCount гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get maxAiCoachCount(): number {
  if (!this.teamPlan && !this.item) {
    return 0;
  }
  const planMax = this.teamPlanAvailability.isAvailable
    ? this.teamPlan?.plan.maxAiCoachs ?? 0
    : 0;
  const itemMax = this.item?.aiCoachAvailableCount ?? 0;
  return planMax + itemMax;
}
```

#### 2.2 зҠ¶ж…ӢеҲӨе®ҡгҒ® getterпјҲenum гғҷгғјгӮ№пјү

**еӨүжӣҙеүҚпјҡ**
```typescript
get teamPlanAvailability(): { isAvailable: boolean; unavailableReason: TranslationKey | null }
get ballAvailability(): { isAvailable: boolean; unavailableReason: TranslationKey | null }
```

**еӨүжӣҙеҫҢпјҡ**
```typescript
/**
 * гғ—гғ©гғігҒ®еҘ‘зҙ„гғ»жңүеҠ№жңҹйҷҗзҠ¶ж…Ӣ
 * Flutter гҒ® teamPlanStatus гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get teamPlanStatus(): TeamPlanStatus {
  // 1. teamPlan гҒҢ null гҒҫгҒҹгҒҜ isActive != true гҒ®е ҙеҗҲ
  if (!this.teamPlan || this.teamPlan.isActive !== true) {
    return TeamPlanStatus.NO_CONTRACT;
  }

  // 2. жңҹйҷҗеҲҮгӮҢгҒӢ
  const isExpired = this.remainingDays <= 0;
  if (isExpired) {
    if (this.nextTeamPlan?.isPendingActivation === true) {
      return TeamPlanStatus.NEXT_PLAN_PENDING;
    }
    return TeamPlanStatus.EXPIRED;
  }

  // 3. жңҹйҷҗиӯҰе‘ҠпјҲ30ж—Ҙд»ҘеҶ…пјү
  if (this.remainingDays <= 30) {
    return TeamPlanStatus.EXPIRING_SOON;
  }

  // 4. е•ҸйЎҢгҒӘгҒ—
  return TeamPlanStatus.OK;
}

/**
 * гғңгғјгғ«и§ЈжһҗгҒ®дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸзҠ¶ж…Ӣ
 * Flutter гҒ® ballAnalysisUsageStatus гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get ballUsageStatus(): BallUsageStatus {
  const usage = this.ballUsage;
  const maxUsage = this.maxBalls;

  // дёҠйҷҗеҲ°йҒ”
  if (usage >= maxUsage) {
    return BallUsageStatus.LIMIT_REACHED;
  }

  // дёҠйҷҗжҺҘиҝ‘пјҲ90%д»ҘдёҠпјү
  if (usage >= Math.floor(maxUsage * 0.9)) {
    return BallUsageStatus.LIMIT_APPROACHING;
  }

  // жӯЈеёё
  return BallUsageStatus.OK;
}

/**
 * AI гӮігғјгғҒгҒ®дҪҝз”ЁйҮҸзҠ¶ж…Ӣ
 * Flutter гҒ® aiCoachUsageStatus гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get aiCoachUsageStatus(): AiCoachUsageStatus {
  const usage = this.aiCoachUsage;
  const maxUsage = this.maxAiCoachCount;

  if (usage >= maxUsage) {
    return AiCoachUsageStatus.LIMIT_REACHED;
  }

  if (usage >= Math.floor(maxUsage * 0.9)) {
    return AiCoachUsageStatus.LIMIT_APPROACHING;
  }

  return AiCoachUsageStatus.OK;
}
```

#### 2.3 еҲ©з”ЁеҸҜеҗҰеҲӨе®ҡгҒ® getter

**ж–°иҰҸиҝҪеҠ пјҡ**
```typescript
/**
 * гғңгғјгғ«и§ЈжһҗгҒҢе®ҹиЎҢеҸҜиғҪгҒӢгҒ©гҒҶгҒӢ
 * Flutter гҒ® canAnalyzeBall гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get canAnalyzeBall(): boolean {
  return ballUsageStatusCanAnalyze(this.ballUsageStatus);
}

/**
 * AI гӮігғјгғҒгҒҢеҲ©з”ЁеҸҜиғҪгҒӢгҒ©гҒҶгҒӢ
 * Flutter гҒ® canUseAiCoach гҒ«еҜҫеҝң
 */
get canUseAiCoach(): boolean {
  return aiCoachUsageStatusCanUse(this.aiCoachUsageStatus);
}
```

#### 2.4 ballRate гҒ®дҝ®жӯЈ

**еӨүжӣҙеүҚпјҡ**
