```typescript
get ballRate(): number {
  const usage = this.ballUsage;
  const maxUsage = this.maxBalls;

  if (maxUsage === 0) {
    return 0;
  }

  const rate = usage / maxUsage;
  return Math.max(0, rate);
}
```

### 3. дҪҝз”Ёз®ҮжүҖгҒ®дҝ®жӯЈ

#### 3.1 `web/src/utils/analysis.util.ts`

**еӨүжӣҙеүҚпјҡ**
