   - Modified `ballRate` to use new `ballUsage` and `maxBalls` getters
   - Added Flutter-aligned getters:
   ```typescript
   // New usage calculation getters (Flutter naming)
   get ballUsage(): number {
     if (!this.teamPlan && !this.item) return 0;
     const planUsage = this.teamPlanAvailability.isAvailable
       ? this.teamPlan?.currentUsage ?? 0 : 0;
     const itemUsage = this.item?.ballUsage ?? 0;
     return planUsage + itemUsage;
